{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3341780/extras/page_descrip_1.png?t=1734997085\" /><i>ITRP _ Vacuum Bless</i> \u2013 research puzzle game about research and puzzles under the nul-gravity conditions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Welcome to the space program!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In the frameworks of this program, you could\u2019ve navigate through endless space, but instead, have to focus on the way to get out of the spaceship which got stuck in space.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Alone within million kilometers</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You have to rely only on yourself. Fortunately, it is enough to manage all the systems of the spaceship. Just study it. Find hidden tunnels and other ways of opening new compartments. Obtain the tackle \u2013 it will help you to reveal your performance limitations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Please, remind me what mission was it\u2026</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Wait, why there are no two-factor security systems on this spaceship? No captain\u2019s cabin? Who has placed so many mysteries here and why? Why does this spaceship completely consist of puzzles? Is this a kind of trick?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Does the rescue shuttle indeed exist?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There is only one way to find it out. Tighten the straps of your overall to navigate in the gravity-free vacuum \u2013 and go ahead to reveal mysteries!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u>Estimated game duration: 4-7 hours.</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3341780/extras/page_door.gif?t=1734997085\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.c